---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Porto Airport Car Rental Comparison | TripAxle"
  description="A practical Porto Airport car rental comparison page for travelers planning northern Portugal trips."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Porto Airport car rental</p>
    <h1>Porto Airport car rental comparison.</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      Use this page to compare booking options, pickup tradeoffs, and common
      rental issues at Porto Airport before you reserve.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="top-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Quick airport summary</h2>
      <p>
        Porto Airport is often a strong pickup point for northern Portugal road
        trips and flexible multi-stop itineraries.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Good fit for northern Portugal routes</li>
        <li>Useful for travelers heading beyond Porto quickly</li>
        <li>May be unnecessary for short city-only stays</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h2>Planned page sections</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Best booking platforms for Porto Airport</li>
        <li>Who should rent immediately and who should wait</li>
        <li>Common pickup and return pain points</li>
        <li>City stay vs road trip decision factors</li>
        <li>What to verify before booking</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="content-grid">
    <article class="main-card">
      <h2>What this page will cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Whether Porto Airport is the right pickup point for your trip</li>
        <li>How airport pickup compares with delaying your rental</li>
        <li>Which traveler types benefit most from renting here</li>
        <li>What to double-check before you reserve</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How this page fits into the site</h2>
      <p>
        This guide will eventually connect to our Portugal overview, airport
        comparison hub, booking-site comparisons, and practical rental guides.
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="side-card">
      <h2>Related Portugal pages</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/portugal-guide">Portugal Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/airport-comparisons">Airport Comparisons</a></li>
        <li><a href="/lisbon-airport-car-rental">Lisbon Airport Car Rental</a></li>
        <li><a href="/faro-airport-car-rental">Faro Airport Car Rental</a></li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem 0 2.25rem;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      color: #2f6fed;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      line-height: 1.08;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #5b5b55;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    .top-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card,
    .main-card,
    .side-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e4e4de;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }

    li + li {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .side-card a {
      color: #2f6fed;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .top-grid,
      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>